* Best Practices\nNotebook Pipelines
** Naming
***_ Descriptive task names
***_ Include layer (bronze_/silver_)
***_ Purpose clear in DAG view
** Organization
***_ Folder hierarchy by pipeline
***_ /pipelines/product/layer/
***_ Team discoverability
** Dependency Design
***_ Only true data relationships
***_ Minimize unnecessary deps
***_ Preserve parallelism
** Output Limits
***_ Cell output ≤ 8 MB
***_ Total notebook output ≤ 20 MB
***_ Write large results to tables
** Git Source
***_ Use workspace notebooks for prod
***_ MLflow tracking requires workspace
@endmindmap
